Info2: <<
Package: itk 
Version: 4.0.0
Revision: 203
Distribution: 10.9, 10.10
Description: Mega-widget support for Tcl 
DescDetail: <<
<<
License: BSD
Homepage: http://incrtcl.sourceforge.net/itcl/ 
Source: mirror:sourceforge:incrtcl/%%5Bincr%%20Tcl_Tk%%5D-4-source/itcl%%204.0.1/itk4.0.0.tar.gz
Source-MD5: c8ffa8df94e4dd02e489d366fd993054
BuildConflicts: lclint
# lclint installs %p/lib/Makefile, which leads configure to believe
# it is using tcltk from tcltk's builddir, hence failure
BuildDepends: tcltk-dev (>= 8.6.2)
Depends: tcltk (>= 8.6.2), %N-shlibs (= %v-%r)
SourceDirectory: %n%v
SetCPP: /usr/bin/cpp
#SetCFLAGS: -DUSE_INTERP_ERRORLINE
SetLDFLAGS: -L%p/lib/itcl%v  -L%p/lib
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p --exec-prefix=%p --mandir=%p/share/man --infodir=%p/share/info --with-tcl=%p/lib --with-tk=%p/lib -with-itcl=%p/lib/itcl4.0.1 -x-includes=/usr/X11R6/include --x-libraries=/usr/X11R6/lib
PatchScript:  <<
perl -pi -e 's,LD_LIBRARY_PATH_VAR="DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH",,' ./configure 
perl -pi -e 's|\@SHLIB_LD\@|\@SHLIB_LD\@  -install_name %p/lib/%n%v/lib%n%v.dylib|g'  Makefile.in
<<
# Testsuite requires access to display but passes
# when run manually.
#InfoTest: TestScript: make test || exit 2
InstallScript: <<
make install DESTDIR=%d
rm -f %i/share/man/mann/toplevel.n
rm -f %i/share/man/mann/widget.n
<<
SplitOff: <<
    Package: %N-shlibs
    Files:<<
        lib/%N%v/lib%N%v.dylib  
    <<
    Shlibs: <<
        %p/lib/%N%v/lib%N%v.dylib                     4.0.0  %n   (>= 4.0.0-1)
    << 
<<
Maintainer: Steffen Schmidt <Steffen.Schmidt@Tuebingen.MPG.de>
SplitOff2: <<
Package: %N-dev
Depends: %N (= %v-%r)
BuildDependsOnly: True
Files: <<   
include/*.h
<<
<<
DescPackaging: <<
Use release tarball. The itcl 4.0.0 release is bundled in the tcltk-8.6.0 packaging.

nieder: Remove widget.n which conflicts with tklib's.
<<
<<
